  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n<!-- Is your feature request related to a specific problem? Is it just a crazy idea? Tell us about it! -->\r\nBools use 8 bit but they only need 1 bit. And it takes 20,000 gas to set a slot from zero to non-zero with SSTORE. So changing a bool field which occupies a whole slot to uint can save a lot of gas.\r\n\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n<!-- Please describe your feature request in detail. -->\r\nIn contracts/security/Pausable.sol:\r\n```\r\nbool private _paused;\r\n```\r\ncan be changed to:\r\n```\r\n    uint256 private constant _PAUSED_FALSE = 1;\r\n    uint256 private constant _PAUSED_TRUE = 2;\r\n    uint256 private _paused;\r\n```\r\n<!-- Make sure that you have reviewed the OpenZeppelin Contracts Contributor Guidelines. -->\r\n<!-- https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md -->\r\n",
